import React from 'react'
import { Link, NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
// import { LOGOUT_USER } from '../utils/mutations'


const Navbar = () => (

    <nav>
      <NavLink activeClassName="active" to="/" className="Home">
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon="fa-solid fa-house" color="#ffffff" />
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink activeClassName="active" className="contact-link" to="/Login">
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon="fa-solid fa-user" color="#ffffff" />
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink activeClassName="active" className="p" to="/predictorpicker">
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon="fa-solid fa-exclamation" color="#ffffff" />
      </NavLink>
    </nav>
)


export default Navbar;
